Package: CopyDetect
Title: Computing Response Similarity Indices for Multiple-Choice Tests
Version: 1.4
Authors@R: person("Cengiz", "Zopluoglu", email = "cengiz@uoregon.edu",
                  role = c("cre","aut"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9397-0262"))
Maintainer: Cengiz Zopluoglu <cengiz@uoregon.edu>
Imports: mirt
Description: Contains several IRT and non-IRT based response similarity indices 
             proposed in the literature for multiple-choice examinations such as 
             the Omega index, Wollack (1997) <doi:10.1177/01466216970214002>; 
             Generalized Binomial Test, van der Linden & Sotaridona (2006) 
             <doi:10.3102/10769986031003283>; K index, K1 and K2 indices, 
             Sotaridona & Meijer (2002) <doi:10.1111/j.1745-3984.2002.tb01138.x>;  
             and S1 and S2 indices, Sotaridona & Meijer (2003) 
             <doi:10.1111/j.1745-3984.2003.tb01096.x>.
